ugin host-hook registration, agent-core tool lookup, cached plugin descriptor execution, static plugin tool registration, bundled capability runtime capture, bundle MCP catalog projection, bundle MCP catalog materialization, Codex dynamic-tool bridge setup, plugin-tools MCP execution, lifecycle/event host-hook registration, session scheduler/action host-hook registration, session extension/trusted policy host-hook registration, reload/node host/node invoke/security audit registration, service/gateway discovery service registration, or command registration completes.\n\nReal environment tested: local focused Vitest through `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs`, local focused lint/format checks, local autoreview, synthetic/private-name scrub, and AWS Crabbox Linux `pnpm check:changed`. Blacksmith Testbox was unavailable in this shell because `blacksmith auth login` is required.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch:\n\n- Force-pushed branch head `9727e0d0fbd`, final rebased onto `origin/main` `1e2fda9e6886`.\n- Latest focused proof after final rebase: `CI=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/config/sessions.cache.test.ts src/plugins/contracts/host-hooks.contract.test.ts extensions/file-transfer/src/shared/node-invoke-policy.test.ts --reporter=verbose`.\n- Latest focused format/diff checks after final rebase: `node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check src/plugins/registry.ts src/plugins/contracts/host-hooks.contract.test.ts src/config/sessions.cache.test.ts extensions/file-transfer/src/shared/node-invoke-policy.test.ts` and `git diff --check`.\n- Latest focused lint after final rebase: `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs src/plugins/registry.ts src/plugins/contracts/host-hooks.contract.test.ts src/config/sessions.cache.test.ts extensions/file-transfer/src/shared/node-invoke-policy.test.ts`.\n- Local review for the command-registration slice: `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode commit --commit HEAD`, run before later drift rebases.\n- Local review for rebase-drift test fixes: `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode commit --commit HEAD`, clean for the session-cache fixture commit and clean for the file-transfer stale-await commit before that cleanup landed on `main`.\n- AWS Crabbox changed gate: `CRABBOX_AWS_REGION=us-east-1 CRABBOX_CAPACITY_REGIONS=us-east-1,us-east-2,us-west-2,eu-west-1,eu-central-1 node scripts/crabbox-wrapper.mjs run --provider aws --shell -- \"corepack pnpm check:changed\"`.\n- Changed-file, spec, and PR-body scrub for the reported plugin name and private path patterns.\n\nEvidence after fix:\n\n- Focused final proof passed after final rebase: 3 files, 117 tests passed.\n- Focused oxfmt check and `git diff --check` passed after final rebase.\n- Targeted oxlint passed after final rebase for `src/plugins/registry.ts`, `src/plugins/contracts/host-hooks.contract.test.ts`, `src/config/sessions.cache.test.ts`, and `extensions/file-transfer/src/shared/node-invoke-policy.test.ts`.\n- Autoreview for the command-registration slice was clean with no accepted/actionable findings.\n- Autoreview for the session-cache fixture drift commit was clean with no accepted/actionable findings.\n- Autoreview for the file-transfer stale-await drift commit was clean before that commit was skipped by the final rebase because equivalent cleanup is already in `main`.\n- AWS Crabbox `check:changed` passed on provider `aws`, lease `cbx_4fdce7317314`, run `run_f0ee5dfc90be`, against base `07870dff45eb` before the final drift rebase.\n- Current branch diff, local spec, and PR body scrub pass for the reported plugin name and private paths.\n\nObserved result after fix:\n\n- Synthetic `fuzzplugin`/`mockplugin` fixtures with unreadable names, schemas, descriptions, approval fields, provider metadata, MCP catalog fields, cached runtime descriptors, Codex dynamic-tool descriptors, MCP argument preparers, Plugin SDK tool metadata, Plugin SDK Control UI descriptors, runtime lifecycle fields, agent event subscription fields, scheduler